          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本宫，孙尚香。兄长孙权，坐镇东吴。自幼喜爱刀枪，深通书史。配于刘皇叔\n玄德为室。只因夫君领兵攻取西川，至今未闻捷报。奴闷坐宫中，十分挂念。\n宫娥们，伺候了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（太监引周善同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启娘娘：东吴周善求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传他进来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传周善进见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周善传入。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周善",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见娘娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周善到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周善",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉太后之命，特来下书。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "书信呈上，下面歇息。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周善",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（太监引周善同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日母后有书信到来，待奴拆开观看便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未曾拆书泪先淋，\n纸上相逢母女情。\n尚香儿从头看分明。\n即速起程莫延停。\n尚香心中暗沉吟。\n恐怕有人阻驾行。\n即刻起驾便登程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传周善。"
        },
        {
          "character": "上写为娘修书信、为母得了思儿病、看罢书信心难忍、皇叔不在荆州郡、低下头来自思忖、四宫女",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传周善。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周善上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周善",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢娘娘酒饭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此时回转东吴，何人保驾？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周善",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为臣保驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "速备船只，即刻起程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周善",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周善下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽无千丈线，万里系人心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四宫女、孙尚香同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "太监→孙尚香",
          "turns": 1
