      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "张飞",
        "报子"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、张飞同上，张飞起霸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "豹头环眼气轩昂，桃园结义世无双。当阳桥前一场战，吓退曹营百万郎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，张飞。如今大哥统领人马，攻取西川。俺奉军师将令，巡查江口，防备东\n吴。远远望见哨探来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀三将军！今有娘娘私抱太子，回转江东，特来报知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可曾报过四将军？"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军师那里，可曾报过？"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未曾报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "速速通报。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！适才探子报道：皇嫂抱定太子，私回东吴，定是孙权之计。俺不免将他\n赶回。\n众将官，带马！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、张飞上马同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
