    {
      "scene_index": 8,
      "label": "第八场",
      "characters_present": [
        "今日过江探母病",
        "君臣无有安身处",
        "周善",
        "娘娘若去留太子",
        "孙尚香",
        "将身跳在船舱外",
        "张飞",
        "我为过江探母病",
        "我若不看大哥面",
        "手使长枪分心刺",
        "赵云",
        "那东吴定下牢笼计"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。四宫女、周善、孙尚香抱子同上，四龙套、赵云同追上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵云为何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘娘哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你无军师命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你无主公差！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言来怒气生，\n大骂常山将赵云。\n苦苦阻拦为何情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "我为过江探母病、赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵云船头打一躬，\n娘娘凤耳听从容：\n皇娘落在圈套中！"
        },
        {
          "character": "那东吴定下牢笼计、孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四叔有所不知情，\n哀家言来听分明：\n骨肉相逢就回程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "今日过江探母病、赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙、刘结仇如山海，\n恐怕一去难回程！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "纲常礼仪全不论，\n刘、孙本是骨肉亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周善",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘娘过江探母病，\n哪个大胆阻路行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言来双眉纵，\n二目圆睁似火红。\n这一枪刺个满江红！"
        },
        {
          "character": "手使长枪分心刺、孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "手使长枪分心刺、孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任你说得天花转，\n哀家只当耳边风！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘娘不与臣作主，\n乌鸦敢入凤凰中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骂一声赵云真大胆，\n此去探病谁敢拦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "临崖勒马收缰晚，\n船到江心补漏难。\n免得为臣挂心间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "娘娘若去留太子、孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自古姣儿不离娘，\n倘有差错谁承当？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘娘此去有人阻，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个敢来阻我行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵云船头来挡驾，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大胆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫非起下反叛心？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘娘若逼臣就死，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不如一死落江心！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘娘投江一死，不致紧要；哪知为臣在那长坂坡前，救幼主的苦处。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有什么苦处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘娘不嫌絮烦，容臣奏来："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵云标英名，娘娘凤耳听！提起长坂事，令人心胆惊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恼刘琮，恨刘琮，\n荆襄九郡归奸雄。\n一齐遘奔在江东。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只杀得："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝剑难入鞘，血染锦战袍。疆场神鬼叫，方显武将高！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣奉命保定甘、糜二位夫人，在乱军之中与甘、糜二位夫人失散。俺行在当阳\n桥，遇见三将军。那时三将军叫道：赵云哪子龙，言说你保的好家眷！问得为\n臣哑口无言。俺只得勒转马头，俺就杀——杀进曹营，寻见了糜夫人，糜夫人\n身带箭伤，怀抱幼主，倒卧尘埃，是俺一见，心如箭攒。那糜夫人看见了为臣\n叫道：赵云哪将军！快快救我母子！那时节曹兵犹如潮水一般，臣杀前不能顾\n后，战左不能顾右。那时为臣奏道：臣保得娘娘，救不得幼主；救得幼主，保\n不得娘娘！好一位糜夫人，解了其情，那时节将幼主交付为臣，那糜夫人她……\n她就投井一死！是臣推墙掩井，怀抱幼主，俺就杀入曹营，不想又得了那贼\n青虹宝剑，俺得此剑，犹如胁生双翼，这远者枪挑，近者剑砍，二次抖擞精神，\n俺就杀杀杀！只杀得真龙出现！"
        },
        {
          "character": "君臣无有安身处、孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是甚等样人，为何真龙出现？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为臣哪有这等造化！乃是幼主真龙出现，那曹操一见现出金龙，当时传下一令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操传下什么将令？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操传将令，晓谕众三军：不许放冷箭，只擒活赵云！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为臣一闻此言，立时哈哈大笑！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你笑者何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "笑只笑只有为臣杀人，并无人来伤我！不想这马不识高低，它就坠……坠落在\n丈二深壑，我君臣眼望苍天无救，忽然西南角下来了一将，打扮大不相同！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他怎样打扮？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来将头戴乌油盔，身披乌油甲，跨下乌骓马，手执皂缨枪，对准为臣，分心就\n刺！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可曾刺着？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是防者不会，会者不防！为臣让过枪头，抓住枪杆，那贼死不放枪，为臣\n死不放手。人借马势，马借人力，俺就纵、纵、纵上了丈二深壑。娘娘，为臣\n在长坂坡前七进七出，好一场厮杀也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（扑灯蛾） 赵云怒气冲，怒气冲，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀得满眼红，满眼红。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一片丹心报主公！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只杀遍地成血海，\n阎罗王差来追魂牌。\n免得为臣挂心怀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "娘娘若去留太子、孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四弟不必多言讲，\n探母一面就回来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问得娘娘无话解，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四弟莫慌，俺张飞来了吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三千岁驾定小舟来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、张飞同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大喝一声把船摇，\n只为皇嫂过江来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇嫂！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你私自过江你大不该！"
        },
        {
          "character": "将身跳在船舱外、孙尚香",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟有所不知情，\n为嫂言来听分明：\n骨肉见面就回程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "今日过江探母病、张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙、刘结仇似山海，\n不该私自过江来！\n一枪刺你穿心怀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "今日过江探母病、张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四弟，何人保驾？"
        },
        {
          "character": "我若不看大哥面、赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周善保驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传周善。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周善上，张飞刺死周善。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去你娘的！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一枪刺死小周善，\n两下分路把船开。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞抢子交赵云。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇嫂！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你死在东吴就莫回来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇嫂做事大不该，不该私自过江来。俺若不看大哥面，一枪刺你穿心怀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺去也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞、赵云抱子、八龙套同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙尚香、四宫女同下。张飞、赵云、八龙套同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好个常山赵子龙，拦江救主立奇功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可笑孙权无见识，周郎妙计一场空！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好吓！好个周郎用计一场空。四弟，你我同见军师缴令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三千岁之功！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四弟之功！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大家之功！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云、张飞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三军的！人马收回！一同缴令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞、赵云、八龙套同下。）"
        }
      ],
